OL,3,CFour deny murder of 17-year-old boy
OL,5,FFour people have pleaded not guilty to
OL,6,Fthe murder of a 17-year-old boy near
OL,7,FCaerphilly in February.
OL,9,FPolice were called to a flat in
OL,10,FAbertridwr on the evening of Thursday,
OL,11,F5 February, when Tristan Shae Kerr was
OL,12,Ffound with stab injuries. He was
OL,13,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,15,FThree men and one woman were charged
OL,16,Fwith murder in connection with his
OL,17,Fdeath, and appeared at Merthyr Crown
OL,18,FCourt on Friday (20 March).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
