OL,3,CFour deny murder of 17-year-old boy
OL,5,FConnor Palfrey, 24 from Abertridwr,
OL,6,Falong with Ricardo Elliot, 27, Georgie
OL,7,FMears, 18, and Elexi Manney, 24, all
OL,8,Fof no fixed abode, all pleaded not
OL,9,Fguilty to murder.
OL,11,FThe four defendants appeared before
OL,12,Fcourt for a plea and trial preparation
OL,13,Fhearing and spoke only to confirm
OL,14,Ftheir names, dates of birth, addresses
OL,15,Fand enter their pleas.
OL,17,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,18,FRecorder of Cardiff, has previously
OL,19,Fset a trial date for 3 August with a
OL,20,Ftime estimate of six weeks.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
