OL,3,CFour deny murder of 17-year-old boy
OL,5,FA pre-trial review hearing will take
OL,6,Fplace on 24 July. Elliot Palfrey,
OL,7,FManny, and Mears were all remanded
OL,8,Finto custody.
OL,10,FIn a previous tribute, the family of
OL,11,FTristan Shae Kerr paid tribute to him,
OL,12,Fdescribing him as "strong, brave and
OL,13,Ffull of warmth".
